OpenVPN setup
=============

1) Install openvpn using standard package manager
2) Generate keys as explained in openvpn docs
3) Copy *.conf to /etc/openvpn (check key configs etc)
4) Copy *.sh and *.py to /etc/openvpn
5) [optional] Copy openvpn.logrotate /etc/logrotate.d/openvpn
6) [optional] Copy openvpn.monit /etc/monit/cond.d/openvpn

$ /etc/init.d/openvpn start|stop

